sudo vim /etc/default/portsentry

change :
TCP_MODE="atcp"
UDP_MODE="audp"

-----------------------------

sudo vim /etc/default/portsentry.conf

change :
BLOCK_UDP="1"
BLOCK_TCP="1"

uncomment chosen kill route and comment the current one (e.g):

KILL_ROUTE="/sbin/iptables -I INPUT -s $TARGET$ -j DROP"

-----------------------------

sudo service portsentry restart"
